00:39:35.310 --> 00:39:43.520
But a published volume followed in
1993 with later editions in 1999,

00:39:43.520 --> 00:39:50.210
2005, 2010, the RNA world
became a plurality of worlds

00:39:50.210 --> 00:39:56.910 position:56%
as new research revealed many new
roles for RNA molecules in the cell.

00:39:56.910 --> 00:40:03.000
Today RNA world denotes a world
of contemporary physiology as much

00:40:03.000 --> 00:40:06.210
as one of chemical evolution.

00:40:06.210 --> 00:40:08.400
RNA world became a mean.

