credit and so forth.

00:41:50.700 --> 00:41:55.070
So my point here, though, is
that nif making has consequences.

00:41:55.070 --> 00:42:01.730
There's a politics and a culture
to which stories are called true.

00:42:01.730 --> 00:42:07.200
So I've shown you several RNA
worlds - the RNA protein world,

00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:13.280
the selfish RNA world, the RNA only
world, and a constructed RNA world.

00:42:13.280 --> 00:42:17.910
All of them are real and
all of them are imagined.

00:42:17.910 --> 00:42:23.560
It's incontrovertible that RNA lies
at the heart of many fundamental

00:42:23.560 --> 00:42:27.740
and ancient biological
processes, and it's nearly certain

00:42:27.740 --> 00:42:30.940
