00:42:30.940 --> 00:42:36.390
But beyond that these are models,
right, they can guide experiments

00:42:36.390 --> 00:42:38.020
but they can never be proven.

00:42:38.020 --> 00:42:39.770
That makes them incredibly
interesting

00:42:39.770 --> 00:42:41.940
as a historical topic, right?

00:42:41.940 --> 00:42:49.140
The plurality of worlds may be,
in fact, not a flaw but a virtue.

00:42:49.140 --> 00:42:53.980
The power of the RNA world may
lie precisely in its ambiguity,

00:42:53.980 --> 00:42:57.010
in its existence as a
kind of virtual reality

00:42:57.010 --> 00:43:00.910
