about these systems,

01:42:16.230 --> 01:42:18.850
whether it's a geothermal
or hydrothermal system,

01:42:18.850 --> 01:42:20.360
is that they're a system in motion.

01:42:20.360 --> 01:42:25.670
So the reaction conditions
that synthesize molecules

01:42:25.670 --> 01:42:29.370
at 300 degrees Celsius or
whatever don't stay in that place

01:42:29.370 --> 01:42:31.780
for any great length of time.

01:42:31.780 --> 01:42:35.510
